Tusk Says Polish Ruling Party ‘Neck-And-Neck’ With Main Rival

-- B y   D a v i d   M c Q u a i d
-- 
2011-09-16T11:26:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/tusk-says-polish-ruling-party-neck-and-neck-with-main-rival.html
Poland’s ruling Civic Platform
party is running “neck-and-neck” with Law & Justice, the
biggest opposition party, making a “surprise” result possible
when the country holds general elections on Oct. 9, Prime
Minister Donald Tusk told reporters today in Gdansk.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David McQuaid at 
 dmcquaid1@bloomberg.net  